core Directory Reference

Open Source Macro Library for Developers of the SAS Language. See: https://github.com/sasjs/core.

More...

Detailed Description

To use - add the subfolders to your SASAUTOS call path.

Directories

 base
 Regular Base SAS Macros.
 
 ddl
 Data Definition Language files.
 
 fcmp
 Macros for generating FCMP functions.
 
 lua
 Lua macros.
 
 meta
 Metadata Aware Macros.
 
 metax
 Metadata Aware Macros with X commmand.
 
 server
 Macros used with sasjs/server
 
 viya
 Viya macros.
 
 xplatform
 Cross Platform, works on all SAS servers (Viya, EBI, SASjs)
